.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-2::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: april, february, may, december, march, october
6 different games are played: snooker, billiard, canasta, monopoly, poker, bridge
 1. the person who's birthday is in december is not the person playing bridge##6
 2. the person playing bridge is in an even position##4
 3. the person playing poker is not to the right of the person playing monopoly##8
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person playing bridge is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person playing billiard##2
 6. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the right of the person playing canasta##5
 7. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##5
 8. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is not the person playing monopoly##6
10. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the left of the person playing canasta##8
12. the person playing bridge is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##8
13. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
14. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
15. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |      3       |   4    |    5    |    6    |
| Birthday   | may | october | february | march | december | april |
| Game     | canasta  | snooker  | billiard         | bridge | poker    | monopoly   |

