 3. the person who likes brown is between the person driving the trike and the person who likes white##2
 4. the person who likes light-blue is in an even position##4
 5. the person who likes brown is somewhere between the person who likes blue and the person driving the train##7
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the left of the person who likes azure##5
 7. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
 8. the person driving the van is not to the left of the person who likes brown##8
 9. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5
10. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the left of the person who likes azure##5
11. the person driving the van is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
12. the person driving the trike is somewhere between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who likes brown##7
13. the person driving the quad-bike is not to the right of the person driving the ship##8
14. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
15. the person driving the quad-bike is in an even position##4
16. the person who likes chestnut is in an even position##4
17. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person who likes brown##5

.:: Answer ::.
