 5. the fan of classical is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the fan of blues is the cape-cod house##1
 7. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
 8. the ranch-style house is not to the left of the futuristic house##8
 9. the ranch-style house is in an even position##4
10. the futuristic house is on the right of the fan of classical##1
11. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
12. the farmhouse house is not to the right of the fan of soul##8

.:: Answer ::.
