.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-18::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: may, december, february, april, january, september
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, aristoff, chaman, dannemann, baccarat, havana
 1. the baccarat-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
 2. the baccarat-smoker is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in september and the aristoff-smoker##7
 3. the baccarat-smoker is not the person who's birthday is in january##6
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##8
 5. the person who's birthday is in april is in an even position##4
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the left of the havana-smoker##8
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
 8. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the aristoff-smoker##5
 9. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5
10. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere to the right of the davidoff-smoker##5
11. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##5
12. the davidoff-smoker is not to the right of the baccarat-smoker##8
13. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the baccarat-smoker##5
14. the davidoff-smoker is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##8
15. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5
16. the davidoff-smoker is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##8
17. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |     2     |   3    |  4   |      5      |   6    |
| Birthday   | january     | april  | september | may  | december | february  |
| Cigar       | davidoff | chaman | havana | baccarat | aristoff | dannemann |

