.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-19::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: water, juice, almond-milk, mirinda, iced-tea, sprite
The people have 6 different jobs:  teacher, security-guard, architect, librarian, pilot, analyst
 1. the analyst is somewhere to the left of the teacher##5
 2. the teacher is not to the left of the person drinking water##8
 3. the person drinking juice is the person drinking juice##1
 4. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the pilot is on the far right##1
 7. the person drinking water is not the pilot##6
 8. the person drinking juice is not to the left of the security-guard##8
 9. the librarian is somewhere to the right of the security-guard##5
10. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
11. the analyst is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
12. the architect is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
13. the architect is not to the right of the teacher##8
14. the librarian is not to the left of the person drinking mirinda##8
15. the security-guard is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
16. the architect is in an odd position##4
17. the person drinking sprite is not to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##8
18. the analyst is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
19. the person drinking juice is not to the right of the architect##8

.:: Answer ::.
