.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-20::.
There 6 different types of food: apricot, banana, potato, strawberry, watermelon, cauliflower
House: ranch-style, townhouse, art-deco, tower, cottage, colonial
 1. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating banana##1
 2. the person eating apricot is not to the right of the tower house##8
 3. the ranch-style house is somewhere to the right of the art-deco house##5
 4. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the left of the person eating potato##5
 5. the tower house is not to the left of the person eating apricot##8
 6. the ranch-style house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 7. the person eating watermelon is somewhere to the right of the ranch-style house##5
 8. the cottage house is not the person eating strawberry##6
 9. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
10. the townhouse house is somewhere to the left of the cottage house##5
11. the person eating watermelon is not the tower house##6
12. the townhouse house is in an odd position##4
13. the ranch-style house is somewhere to the right of the person eating banana##5
14. the tower house is in an odd position##4
15. the colonial house is somewhere to the right of the ranch-style house##5
16. the colonial house is the person eating watermelon##1
17. the person eating potato is somewhere to the right of the person eating strawberry##5
18. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the left of the person eating potato##5
19. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
20. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
21. the colonial house is not to the left of the person eating strawberry##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |    3    |     4     |     5      |   6   |
| Food   | apricot | banana | strawberry | potato     | watermelon | cauliflower   |
| House   | tower      | art-deco | townhouse    | ranch-style | colonial     | cottage |

 